ALGORITHIM

Ask user to enter divident
Set Answer to divident modulus 2
IF Answer is equal to zero then
Display the divident is an even number
Else display the the divident is an odd number

## Another method
Ask user to enter number
SET Result as integer
Divide number by 2 and store it in Result
multiply 2 by Result and store it in Result2
subtract number from Result2 and store it in Result3
If Result3 is equal to zero it means the number is even else the number is odd 
